{"prompt": "Generate a website for a sustainable fashion brand. The website should be sophisticated and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Evergreen Threads</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #8B0000; /* Dark Red */\n            --secondary-color: #D3D3D3; /* Light Gray */\n            --background-color: #F5F5DC; /* Beige */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --accent-color: #A0522D; /* Sienna */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-color);\n            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 3rem 1rem;\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--accent-color));\n            color: var(--background-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .hero h3 {\n            font-size: 2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .collections img {\n            width: 100%;\n            max-width: 300px;\n            height: auto;\n            display: block;\n            margin: 1rem auto;\n            border: 3px solid var(--primary-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n        }\n\n        .collections .item {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .collections h4 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            border-top: 5px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Evergreen Threads</h1>\n    </header>\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        <a href=\"#collections\">Collections</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"hero\">\n            <h3>Style That Grows On You</h3>\n            <p>Discover conscious fashion that blends timeless design with eco-friendly practices. Wear your values.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Story</h2>\n            <p>At Evergreen Threads, we believe in a future where fashion doesn't cost the Earth. We meticulously source sustainable materials and partner with ethical manufacturers to bring you beautiful, durable clothing. Our commitment is to transparency, quality, and a slower, more mindful approach to style.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"collections\" class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Collections</h2>\n            <div class=\"collections\">\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/8B0000/F5F5DC?text=Serene+Spring\" alt=\"Serene Spring Collection\">\n                    <h4>Serene Spring Collection</h4>\n                    <p>Lightweight, organic fabrics perfect for warmer days.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/A0522D/F5F5DC?text=Autumn+Elegance\" alt=\"Autumn Elegance Collection\">\n                    <h4>Autumn Elegance Collection</h4>\n                    <p>Cozy knits and rich textures crafted from recycled materials.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/8B0000/D3D3D3?text=Timeless+Essentials\" alt=\"Timeless Essentials Collection\">\n                    <h4>Timeless Essentials Collection</h4>\n                    <p>Versatile pieces designed to be the foundation of your sustainable wardrobe.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Have questions or want to learn more about our process? We'd love to hear from you.</p>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@evergreenthreads.com\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color); text-decoration: underline;\">info@evergreenthreads.com</a></p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Evergreen Threads. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}